82
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,670
If someone ever bullies you,

83
00:06:17,950 --> 00:06:19,070
I'll be first to defend you.

84
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:28,510
I'm glad you're safe.

85
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:30,790
