91
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:42,480
It's okay, Jing Xin.

92
00:06:43,670 --> 00:06:46,040
I know you care about me.

93
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:49,230
By the way, when we're alone,

94
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,790
