207
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:20,970
(Intimate contact with another bachelor.
Sent an expensive gift to a bachelor.)

208
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:22,380
(Peeking a bachelor.)

209
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:26,710
