224
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:18,520
(Whatever. I just have to get this man first.)

225
00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:19,550
Of course, I do.

226
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:20,840
I'm very much

227
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,640
